{
 "name": "RPlog_Destruction_of_Garrison_Vexed",
 "title": "The Destruction of Garrison Vexed",
 "summary": "Task Force Inquisitor, the loyalist Imperial fleet under Captain Jal'Dana, Commodore Inrokana, and Krieg, launches a coordinated assault to wipe out Garrison Vexed, the last stronghold of the renegade Danik regime. On the ground, infiltrator Dreven sabotages the base shield generator, opening the way for stormtroopers of the 501st Legion led by Rei'yak (Cardila) and medic Drogyn to storm the garrison against fanatical defenders, hidden AT-AT walkers, and impressed civilian militia. In orbit, the loyalists crush the Neo-Imperial corvettes and a surprise relief force of mercenary cruisers, while New Republic pilots of Ghost Squadron, Kyrin Sh'vani, Raxis, and Lance, exploit the chaos to gather intelligence and shepherd a freighter of refugees to safety amid a sprawling dogfight with the TIE Interceptors of Dante and Liza Molokai. The garrison falls, its walkers destroyed and its surviving traitors captured or executed, while the last mercenary cruiser surrenders unconditionally. The operation ends as a total Imperial victory, leaving the Danik movement extinguished at heavy but one-sided cost.",
